<section id="content">

<blockquote>
	<q>There are two golden rules for an orchestra: start together and finish together. The public doesn&#39;t give a damn what goes on in between.</q>
	<cite><a href="/author/134">Sir Thomas Beecham</a></cite>
	<footer>contributed by <a href="/contributor/38">Eric Cavanaugh</a></footer>
</blockquote>

